    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《梦幻零号频道》（Dream Channel Zero），是被困在游戏世界的青年“小哲”，与身着连帽衫的少女“琉美”相遇，一起克服种种困难、努力逃离游戏世界的故事。这个混杂着“欢笑、泪水和恐怖”的另类游戏世界，作为一款全新感觉的冒险游戏，由《Zelle》的开发者Fuming和Odencat联袂呈现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-游戏特点-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382810/extras/0b045de3ad3b4234d83655fcec36aeca.poster.avif?t=1757713351\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382810/extras/0b045de3ad3b4234d83655fcec36aeca.webm?t=1757713351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382810/extras/0b045de3ad3b4234d83655fcec36aeca.mp4?t=1757713351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无限可能、令人期待的世界地图！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小小的角色，冒险时会做出许多动作哦，很可爱的！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >停止节点上时，可能会发生支线剧情，移动到各种地方，比如角色们的家里哦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382810/extras/4a27075398ea895df0875e26d7db0059.poster.avif?t=1757713351\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382810/extras/4a27075398ea895df0875e26d7db0059.webm?t=1757713351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382810/extras/4a27075398ea895df0875e26d7db0059.mp4?t=1757713351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作场景里的电视机，切换到其他频道，就可以瞬间移动到别的世界呢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从人见人爱的夏日海滩，到暗无天日的夜色世界，世界观各具特色的许多频道，等你来探险哦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382810/extras/6179545228dc58eb9cc41321409af441.poster.avif?t=1757713351\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382810/extras/6179545228dc58eb9cc41321409af441.webm?t=1757713351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382810/extras/6179545228dc58eb9cc41321409af441.mp4?t=1757713351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被称作“恶灵”的角色们，在这个世界里四处游荡哦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要碰上了就会“战斗”，非常简单而且爽快的那种！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的反射神经，够不够用啊？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不管敌人的招式有多少套路，见招拆招，再让他们尝尝你拳头的厉害吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382810/extras/62db228e53aad22bd6d7f51c91c66795.avif?t=1757713351\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很有料的居民们，在这个世界里等着你呐……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就连NPC，也全是看起来就很个性的家伙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个游戏里，所有的角色都是主角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382810/extras/77abf84cd50ce1159283e64075c2297d.poster.avif?t=1757713351\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382810/extras/77abf84cd50ce1159283e64075c2297d.mp4?t=1757713351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然本作中有许多荒诞笑哏，但是危险的气息仍然无处不在……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个世界的每个频道中，都有相当于“Boss”的人物存在，而在他们的背景中，又有各种各样的故事若隐若现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和小哲、琉美一起，揭开这个世界的谜底吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随时兴奋不已、心跳不停的大冒险，就要开始了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
